mer-uuvm1b" data-framer-name="Case-Study (section 2)"><div class="framer-2dajyf" data-framer-name="Text"><div class="framer-50vbi4" data-framer-name="Details"><div class="framer-1goam4n" data-framer-appear-id="1goam4n" data-framer-name="Challenges" style="opacity:0.001;transform:perspective(1200px) translateY(40px)"><div class="framer-nsbesf" data-framer-name="Challenges" data-framer-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><h2 class="framer-text framer-styles-preset-1m9bzi2" data-styles-preset="stylesPresetHeading2" style="--framer-text-color:var(--token-f4c5cb3c-d0fa-4ab5-930d-a0f44660151c, rgb(30, 27, 75))">Objectives and challenges</h2></div><div class="framer-ied4gf"><div class="framer-lipu3u"><div class="framer-tr6hny" data-framer-name="Complex Feature Integration: Implementing robust features such as real-time workout tracking, personalized coaching insights, and social sharing capabilities. User-Centric Design: Designing an intuitive interface that caters to users of varying fitness levels, from beginners to advanced athletes. Scalability: Ensuring the app can handle a growing user base and future updates without compromising performance." data-framer-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><h5 class="framer-text framer-styles-preset-1n1ski5">Brand Cohesion: Designed graphic elements that maintained the essence of Colombia 4.0.</h5></div></div><div class="framer-9lkh18"><div class="framer-s7flvj" data-framer-name="Complex Feature Integration: Implementing robust features such as real-time workout tracking, personalized coaching insights, and social sharing capabilities. User-Centric Design: Designing an intuitive interface that caters to users of varying fitness levels, from beginners to advanced athletes. Scalability: Ensuring the app can handle a growing user base and future updates without compromising performance." data-framer-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><h5 class="framer-text framer-styles-preset-1n1ski5">Event Coverage: Created real-time graphics and social media posts during the event.</h5></div></div><div class="framer-mobwn6"><div class="framer-190cusd" data-framer-name="Complex Feature Integration: Implementing robust features such as real-time workout tracking, personalized coaching insights, and social sharing capabilities. User-Centric Design: Designing an intuitive interface that caters to users of varying fitness levels, from beginners to advanced athletes. Scalability: Ensuring the app can handle a growing user base and future updates without compromising performance." data-framer-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><h5 class="framer-text framer-styles-preset-1n1ski5">Agenda and Guests: Supported agenda development and designed materials for invited speakers.</h5></div></div></div></div><div class="framer-1inb2pe" data-framer-name="My Approach" style="will-change:transform;opacity:0;transform:perspective(1200px) translateY(40px)"><div class="framer-65nia0" data-framer-name="My Approach" data-framer-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><h3 class="framer-text framer-styles-preset-ci2ngw" data-styles-preset="stylesPresetHeading3">My approach</h3></div><div class="framer-13k9fak" data-framer-name="Discovery Phase Market Research: Conducted thorough market analysis to understand user needs, competitor offerings, and emerging trends in fitness app development. User Persona Development: Created detailed user personas to guide design and feature prioritization. Design and Development UI/UX Design: Designed a clean and intuitive interface with easy navigation and visually appealing graphics to motivate users. Feature Implementation: Developed and integrated key features like GPS tracking, workout history, customized training plans, and in-app social sharing. Backend Development: Built a scalable backend infrastructure to support real-time data synchronization and user analytics. Testing and Iteration User Testing: Conducted extensive usability testing with target users to gather feedback and refine the app interface and functionality. Performance Optimization: Implemented optimizations for speed, reliability, and security to ensure a seamless user experience." data-framer-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><ol class="framer-text"><li data-preset-tag="p" class="framer-text framer-styles-preset-16bzrdu"><p class="framer-text framer-styles-preset-16bzrdu">Discovery Phase</p></li></ol><ul class="framer-text"><li data-preset-tag="p" class="framer-text framer-styles-preset-16bzrdu"><p class="framer-text framer-styles-preset-16bzrdu"><strong class="framer-text">Graphic Concept Ideation</strong>: I developed graphic proposals for the development of the event Colombia 4.0</p></li><li data-preset-tag="p" class="framer-text framer-styles-preset-16bzrdu"><p class="framer-text framer-styles-preset-16bzrdu"><strong class="framer-text">Concept Development</strong>: Based on the selected graphic proposal, the construction of the graphic universe and its applications across different media begins.</p></li></ul><ol start="2" class="framer-text"><li data-preset-tag="p" class="framer-text framer-styles-preset-16bzrdu"><p class="framer-text framer-styles-preset-16bzrdu">Design and Development</p></li></ol><ul class="framer-text"><li data-preset-tag="p" class="framer-text framer-styles-preset-16bzrdu"><p class="framer-text framer-styles-preset-16bzrdu"><strong class="framer-text">Development of Pieces for Social Media</strong>: Pieces were designed for promotion on social media in previous phases, during, and after the event.</p></li><li data-preset-tag="p" class="framer-text framer-styles-preset-16bzrdu"><p class="framer-text framer-styles-preset-16bzrdu"><strong class="framer-text">Agenda and Speakers Design</strong>: Part of COl40's success lies in the quality of its speakers, bringing in current references from the creative world, designing promotional pieces for the speakers was a fundamental part of promoting the event on social media.</p></li><li data-preset-tag="p" class="framer-text framer-styles-preset-16bzrdu"><p class="framer-text framer-styles-preset-16bzrdu"><strong class="framer-text">'In situ' Support</strong>: During the event, additional pieces were required for promotion at key moments, such as photos during presentations to encourage potential attendees to interact, as well as leaving graphic records for future event promotions.</p></li></ul></div></div><div class="framer-iok154" data-framer-name="gallery-image-s"><div class="ssr-variant"><div class="framer-1s17bho" data-framer-name="gallery-Image-s1" style="will-change:transform;opacity:0;transform:perspective(1200px) translateY(40px)"><div style="position:absolute;border-radius:inherit;corner-shape:inherit;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;left:0" data-framer-background-image-wrapper="true"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="801" sizes="(min-width: 1440px) max((max(min(100vw * 0.96, 100vw) * 0.8 - 64px, 1px) - 24px) / 2, 50px), (min-width: 810px) and (max-width: 1439.98px) max((max(min((100vw - 64px) * 0.96, 100vw - 64px) * 0.8 - 64px, 1px) - 24px) / 2, 50px), (max-width: 809.98px) max(min((100vw - 32px) * 0.96, 100vw - 32px) * 0.8 - 64px, 50px)" srcset="https://framerusercontent.com/images/p5ewqLR1TCdosPOytM1oHaZUse4.jpg?scale-down-to=512&amp;width=1200&amp;height=801 512w,https://framerusercontent.com/images/p5ewqLR1TCdosPOytM1oHaZUse4.jpg?scale-down-to=1024&amp;width=1200&amp;height=801 1024w,https://framerusercontent.com/images/p5ewqLR1TCdosPOytM1oHaZUse4.jpg?width=1200&amp;height=801 1200w" src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/p5ewqLR1TCdosPOytM1oHaZUse4.jpg?width=1200&amp;height=801" alt style="display:block;width:100%;height:100%;border-radius:inherit;corner-shape:inherit;object-position:center;object-fit:cover"></div></div></div><div class="ssr-variant"><div class="framer-i5punv" data-framer-name="gallery-Image-s2" style="will-change:transform;o